beer.beer_description: Our Even Keel is a hoppy ale designed for smooth sailing. A full-flavored beer with a silky malt backbone and a bright hop profile of herbs and citrus, it packs all the taste of an IPA in  a session able alchohol content. This ale is perfect for leisurely days on the water, when all you want are a few beers and a level ride.
